deck: D.M. Higgins is a comic book writer, editor, and letterer currently based in Montreal, Canada. Higgins has a master's degree in visual communication and currently serves as editor and publisher of Superdames Comics, an independent publisher of titles that celebrate female characters with a progressive outlook (most notably, the "Jill Trent, Science Sleuth" reboot). Higgins has also worked with Cloudscape Comics and other independent publishers.
